<xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" n="sb;3;6756" targOrder="U" to="DITTO" type="reprint from">SB3,6756;PEdg50</xref></head><div lang="grc" part="N" type="edition"><div n="r" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="1"/>Κρίτων Μοσχίωνι χ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">α</unclear>ί<supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ρει</supplied>ν. ἐνέτυχεν ἡμῖν Δημοκράτης 

    <lb n="2"/>ὁ ἀποδιδούς σοι τὴ<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ν</unclear> <supplied cert="high" reason="lost">ἐπισ</supplied>τολὴν φάμενος ἀδικεῖσθαι ὑπὸ 

    <lb n="3"/>Φιλοκλέους τοῦ τοπαρχοῦντος ὑπὸ σὲ καὶ <choice><corr>ἀφῃρῆσθαι</corr><sic>αφειρησθαι</sic></choice> αὐτοῦ 

    <lb n="4"/>πυρῶν <expan><ex cert="high">ἀρτάβας</ex></expan> <num value="50">ν</num>, οὐκ ὀφείλοντος αὐτοῦ τῶι βασιλεῖ οὐθὲν οὐδὲ 

    <lb n="5"/>γεγεωργηκότος <choice><corr>ὑπ᾽</corr><sic>υφ</sic></choice> αὐτόν, ἀλλὰ <choice><corr>συνηγορακὼς</corr><sic>συνηραγορακως</sic></choice> παρὰ τῶν 

    <lb n="6"/>θεριστῶν. καλῶς ἂν οὖν ποιήσαις φροντίσας περὶ αὐτοῦ 

    <lb n="7"/>ὅπως ἂν κομίσηται καὶ μὴ ἀδικηθῆι. <del rend="erasure">καὶ</del> φησὶ δὲ καὶ ὑπ᾽ ἄλλων 

    <lb n="8"/>τινῶν ἀδικεῖσθαι τῶν ὑπὸ σέ. σὺ οὖν μὴ ἐπίτρεπε αὐτοῖς· 

    <lb n="9"/><choice><corr>ἔστιν</corr><sic>εστιγ</sic></choice> γὰρ παρ᾽ ἡμῶν. 

    <lb n="10"/>ἔρρωσο. <expan><ex cert="high">ἔτους</ex></expan> <num value="36">λϛ</num>, Τῦβι <num value="15">ιε</num>. 
</ab></div><div n="v" part="N" type="textpart"><ab part="N">

    <lb n="11"/>Μοσχί<unclear cert="high" reason="undefined">ωνι</unclear>. </ab></div></div><div n="meta.966" part="N" type="description"><p><rs cert="high" type="material">Papyrus</rs></p></div><div n="meta.966" part="N" subtype="textDate" type="commentary"><p><date notAfter="-249" notBefore="-249" type="textDate" value="-0249-03-07">7. März 249 v.Chr.</date></p></div><div n="meta.966" part="N" subtype="principalEdition" type="bibliography"><listBibl><bibl subtype="principal" type="publication"><title level="s" type="abbreviated">P.Cair. Zen.</title><biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope><biblScope type="numbers">59322</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="Trismegistos"><biblScope type="numbers">966</biblScope></bibl><bibl type="DDbDP"><series>0092</series>; <biblScope type="volume">3</biblScope>; <biblScope type="numbers">59322</biblScope></bibl></listBibl><p>Perseus links: <xref evaluate="all" from="ROOT" href="0092;3;59322" targOrder="Y" to="DITTO" type="Perseus">Text in Perseus</xref></p></div><div n="meta.966" part="N" subtype="illustrations" type="bibliography"><p>keine</p></div><div n="meta.966" part="N" subtype="otherPublications" type="bibliography"><head>Andere Publikation</head><bibl subtype="other" type="publication">SB III 6756</bibl></div><div n="meta.966" part="N" subtype="translations" type="bibliography"><head>Übersetzungen</head><listBibl lang="en"><head lang="de">Englisch:</head><bibl type="translations">C.C. Edgar, ASAE 20, 1920, S. 24</bibl></listBibl></div><div n="meta.966" part="N" subtype="locations" type="history"><p>unbekannt</p></div><div n="meta.966" part="N" type="figure"><p><figure href="http://ipap.csad.ox.ac.uk/4DLink4/4DACTION/IPAPwebquery?vPub=P.Cair.Zen.&amp;vVol=3&amp;vNum=59322"><figDesc>Abbildung im Internet</figDesc></figure></p></div></body></text></TEI.2>